<h2 id="get-started-with-piperider">Get started with PipeRider</h2>

<p>As I mentioned above, if you‚Äôre a dbt user then PipeRider should be your go-to data reliability tool.  If you already have a dbt project, all you need to do is <a href="https://docs.piperider.io/cli/dbt-integration">initialize PipeRider inside the project</a> and your data source settings will be automatically detected:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># inside your dbt project folder</span>
piperider init
</code></pre></div></div>
